data.description: Massive price reduction!  Stylishly renovated two-level Westwood Park home with gleaming bamboo floors, chef's kitchen, high-end stainless steel appliances, quartz counter tops, two flat screen TVs, modern lighting, luxury baths & laundry room.  This beautiful home is bright, spacious and detached on all sides.  Ample cabinetry and lots of storage.  Built on an extra large lot allowing for numerous possibilities!  Close to Whole Foods, restaurants, shops, cafes, Ingleside public library, City College, 24 Hour Fitness and Yoga Flow SF. Public transportation within two blocks.  Easy freeway access.
